# what is CSS

CSS is a language used inside html to style html structure.

the language of CSS is broken into modules and many of the doucmentation pages are organized around a particular module to find out what its purpose is the different properties and features it contains.

There are three ways to add CSS style sheet
    1- External CSS
    2-  Internal CSS
    3-  Inline CSS

With External you can change the look of an entire website by changing just onoe file.

Internal style sheet maybe used if one single HTML page has a unique style and the internal style is placed inside the head section.

An Inline style maybe used to apply a unique style for a single element. You add the style attribute to the relevent element and the style attribute can contain any CSS property.